2026-05-04

Scope:
- Minimal FinanceBench / financial RAG retrieval adjustment.
- Only prioritize existing page index table_text.
- No OCR, no hi_res parsing dependency, no table-system refactor.

Changed files:
- backend/rag_utils.py

Changes:
- Added a small page-level table signal score when a page already has non-empty table_text.
- The table signal is derived from overlap between query metrics / numbers / years / tokens and the existing table_text only.
- Added a modest score bonus so pages with relevant existing table_text are ranked ahead of similar pages without it.
- Strengthened final_evidence_pack_used ordering so relevant table_text entries on matched pages are preferred earlier.
- Exposed has_table_text and table_signal_score in page_scores for easier debugging.
